precis:
Amendments to the PACIFIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1993 which will permit the
Director General - Pacific Region to determine quotas and fishing seasons
as well as size and weight limits previously fixed under the International
Pacific Halibut Convention Regulations, and to attach conditions to
licences.
